description: I would call it "cute tourist got lucky, or...?". It was one of first nice spring days so with great mood I went out for a hunt. With new season the game is as well waking up and looking for a way to get money to enjoy warm summer days which are about to come. I´ve been very lucky cause I´ve met just the perfect match for my today´s needs. Cutie from south of Czech Republic. Just wandering around Prague. He was amazingly sweet, tall and young. Already after his studies and without a job. It seemed as most easiest convincing ever. But there was a catch cause his family was rich and he had a source of money even without a job. knew that he won´t say no to get something very easy and fast. It was just a matter of finding a right amount and we ended up in a hotel room. Soon after  he was jerking me off and it didn´t take me long to get him on his knees with my dick in his mouth.
title: Czech Hunter 187
